{"componentChunkName":"component---src-markdown-template-js","path":"/v1.0/components/notice-box","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1>알림 박스 (notice-box)</h1>\n<p>짧은 메세지 같은 간단한 내용을 일정시간동안 화면 상단에 띄울때 사용합니다.</p>\n<h2>알림</h2>\n<p>알림을 띄울 버튼에 <code class=\"language-text\">data-toggle=&quot;notice&quot;</code> 를 입력해주며, <code class=\"language-text\">.notice-box</code> 값을 가지고 있는 요소를 <code class=\"language-text\">data-target</code>에 id값을 입력해줍니다.</p>\n<div class=\"card\">\n<div class=\"card-body\">\n<button class=\"btn btn-brown\" data-toggle=\"notice\" data-target=\"#exampleNoticeBox00\">Notice-Box</button>\n<div class=\"notice-box\" id=\"exampleNoticeBox00\" data-speed=\"4000\">\n\tThis is Notice-Box\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>button</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>btn btn-brown<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">data-toggle</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>notice<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">data-target</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>#exampleNoticeBox00<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Notice-Box<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>notice-box<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>exampleNoticeBox00<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">data-speed</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>4000<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\tThis is Notice-Box\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n</div>\n<h2>애니메이션 속도 조정</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">data-speed</code> 값을 변경함으로서 애니메이션 속도를 조정할수있습니다.\ndefault 값은 4000, 즉 4초를 가지고 있습니다.</p>\n<div class=\"card\">\n<div class=\"card-body\">\n<button class=\"btn btn-brown\" data-toggle=\"notice\" data-target=\"#exampleNoticeBox01\">Notice-Box 1000</button>\n<div class=\"notice-box\" id=\"exampleNoticeBox01\" data-speed=\"1000\">\n\tThis is Notice-Box\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>button</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>btn btn-brown<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">data-toggle</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>notice<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">data-target</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>#exampleNoticeBox01<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Notice-Box 1000<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>notice-box<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>exampleNoticeBox01<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">data-speed</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>1000<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\tThis is Notice-Box\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n</div>","frontmatter":{"version":"v1.0","slug":"/components/notice-box","title":"알림"}}},"pageContext":{"version":"v1.0","slug":"/components/notice-box","vIntroduction":"v1.0/introduction","vUtilities":"v1.0/utilities","vComponents":"v1.0/components"}},"staticQueryHashes":["63159454","782063376"]}